body:
As the title suggests, I really want to know why she hasn't gotten lore, or at least some fan made stuff. Aery stands out from the other runes, she is a living thing (or a spirit, if you don't classify that as living). When I think of Aery, Zephyr also comes to mind, Zephyr meaning a soft breeze, while Aery is an adjective; characterized by lightness and insubstantiality; as impalpable or intangible as air. Both related to wind/air etc. Basically, I just want to know what is Aery exactly? and where does she come from? 



